This configuration sets up an OpenSearch Serverless domain and a Kinesis Firehose Delivery Stream with an OpenSearch Serverless destination. It also includes necessary IAM roles and policies for the Firehose to access the OpenSearch domain. Be sure to replace `"us-west-2"` with your desired AWS region and adjust any parameters as necessary for your setup.

