**Notes**:
- Replace `"your-key-name"` with the appropriate EC2 key pair name in your AWS account.
- Update the `ami` with a suitable AMI ID, depending on your AWS region and needs.
- Consider setting up additional security measures or customizations per real-world requirements.
- The placement group strategy is set to `"cluster"` for low-latency network performance among the instances within the same group.

